reviewText: I was really liking this DVD until about 1:30:00 in then I heard that whiny voice. Waddie Mitchell. My heart sank. Why do they keep putting that arrogant SOyouknowhat in DVDs about Texas cowpunchers? The rest of the video was worth five stars but Waddie Mitchell was a three star deduction.
Very good, many similarities to the western culture here

You feel like you are right there in the open range - dust and all. I have the rest of the series - enjoyed everyone of them. This is our heritage boys & girls and J&S have captured this essence of Americana.
